Comment.value: This is the mini plot involving Bertrand who is waiting for his brother at the Helmite shrine.
This is the plot involving Aldo and his halfling family. They are guarding their wagon and waiting for news of Hector, a servant sent for parts. They will not leave without news of him.
This is the plot that you get by talking to Ergus or Walters. Walters has gone missing and needs to be returned to the Gate.
